data.description: You won't want to miss this amazing 2-story home in Meridian Ranch! It has it all... 5 bedrooms, 4 baths PLUS an office...upgraded appliances, quartz and granite counters throughout...walkout basement, backs to open space... The main level boast of Wood Floors in Entry, Kitchen and Dining nook; office, Open Concept living area; Gourmet Kitchen with State of the Art JennAir Microwave, Dishwasher, Gas Range/Double Oven and and LG "Knock-twice" light up window Refrigerator and guest bath. The Upper level features the majority of the bedrooms. Here you will find the Primary Bedroom with attached 5-piece bath, 2 closets and Pikes Peak views, three additional bedrooms, a full hall bath and the conveniently located upper-level laundry. The walkout basement is a perfect entertainment mecca or Guest retreat complete with Family/Recreation room, Wet Bar, 5th Bedroom, bath with custom-tiled shower with rain shower head, under stair storage and walkout to an amazing backyard oasis. The home backs to open space, leaving a private setting with eastern plains views. A wonderful dry creek bed with bridge, raised gardens, String Lights and a concrete pad and 220V means its Hot Tub ready! Close to Parks, Schools and the Falcon Dog Park and Meridian Rach Rec Center. Easy commute to Schriever AFB, Peterson AFB and the Powers Corridor. A little jaunt through Black Forest brings you right to the Air Force Academy and I-25.
